---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateCTA from '../../components/AffiliateCTA.astro';
import { AFFILIATE_LINKS as affiliates } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const title = 'Free AI Website Builders: What is the Catch? (2025)';
const description = 'All AI website builders offer "free" plans. Here is what they actually give you, what they withhold, hidden costs, and when you really need to pay.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">GUIDE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Free AI Website Builders: What is the Catch?</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Free plans are freemium models. Limited features, forced branding, and upgrade pressure. Here is the reality behind "free."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Summary -->
    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">The Truth About Free Plans</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">üéØ Best Use Case</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Testing builders before committing. Build your site, see if you like it, then upgrade for launch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">‚ö†Ô∏è Main Catch</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">You'll need to pay to actually launch professionally: no custom domain, builder branding, limited features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">üí∞ Typical Cost</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">$9-25/month for plans that include custom domain and remove branding.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What Free Plans Include -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Free Plans Actually Include</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">‚úÖ What You Get</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>AI generation</strong> - Full access to AI site building features</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Basic templates</strong> - Access to template library (sometimes limited)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Hosting</strong> - Your site is live on a subdomain (yoursite.builder.com)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Storage</strong> - 50-500MB (enough for text + some images)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Basic support</strong> - Email support (slow response times)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Basic analytics</strong> - Page view tracking (sometimes limited)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-red-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">‚ùå What's Missing</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Custom domain</strong> - Stuck with buildername.com/yoursitename</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>No branding</strong> - "Built with XYZ" footer you can't remove</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Limited pages</strong> - Some cap at 1-3 pages on free</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>No e-commerce</strong> - Can't sell products or collect payments</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Limited forms</strong> - Contact form submissions capped or removed</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Slow support</strong> - Paid users get priority</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>No SSL/HTTPS</strong> - Some builders reserve this for paid (rare now)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Free Plan Comparison -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Free Plan Comparison: Popular Builders</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Builder</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Free Pages</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Storage</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Custom Domain</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Branding</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold"><a href="/reviews/durable-ai" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Durable ‚Üí</a></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Unlimited (30 days)</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Full</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">‚ùå No</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold"><a href="/reviews/mixo-ai" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Mixo ‚Üí</a></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Unlimited</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Full</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">‚ùå No</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold"><a href="/reviews/webflow-ai" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Webflow ‚Üí</a></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Unlimited</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">1GB</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">‚ùå No</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold"><a href="/reviews/wix-ai" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Wix ‚Üí</a></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Unlimited</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">500MB</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">‚ùå No</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Included</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold"><a href="/reviews/hostinger-ai" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Hostinger ‚Üí</a></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Unlimited</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Limited</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">‚ùå No</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Included</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4 italic">Note: Most builders require paid plan for custom domain (yoursite.com). Free plans use subdomains (yoursite.builder.com).</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Hidden Costs -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Hidden Costs of "Free" Plans</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">üí∞ Upgrade Traps</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Domain costs</strong> - Even paid plans may not include free domain ($10-15/year extra)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Overage fees</strong> - Exceed storage/visitor limits = surprise charges</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Feature unlock</strong> - Want email forms? SEO tools? That's an upsell.</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Price increases</strong> - Introductory rates jump after year 1 (50-100% hikes common)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Exit costs</strong> - Migrating away means rebuilding content (no clean export)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">üéØ The Freemium Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Why do builders offer free plans? It's a customer acquisition strategy:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Get you hooked on their platform</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Make it painful to switch (lock-in)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Upsell once you've invested time building</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Free users provide product feedback and word-of-mouth marketing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- When Free is Actually Enough -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">When Free Plans Are Actually Enough</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">‚úÖ Stick with Free If:</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Testing/learning - Experimenting with AI builders</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Personal projects - Hobbies, portfolios that don't need pro branding</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Temporary sites - Event pages, coming soon, short-term campaigns</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Prototype phase - Proof of concept before budget approval</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Students/learning - Building skills without financial commitment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">üí° Pro Tip: Use Free Trials Strategically</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Most builders offer 14-30 day FULL trials (not just free plans). Test everything with premium features enabled, then downgrade to free or decide to pay.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- When to Upgrade -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">When You MUST Upgrade</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="bg-red-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">üö® Pay When:</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Launching a business</strong> - Builder branding = unprofessional</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Need custom domain</strong> - yoursite.com not yoursite.builder.com</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>SEO matters</strong> - Subdomains rank worse, branded subdomains look spammy</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>E-commerce</strong> - Need to sell products? Free plans won't cut it</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Client work</strong> - Can't deliver site with another company's branding</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Remove limitations</strong> - Page caps, storage limits, form submission caps</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Best Free Options -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Best Free Plans (Ranked)</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">ü•á Durable - 30 Day Free Trial</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Full access to all features for 30 days</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/reviews/durable-ai" class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">READ REVIEW ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-3">Best for: Thorough testing. Generous trial lets you actually build and launch before deciding.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">ü•à Webflow - Unlimited Free Plan</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Keep sites free forever (with branding)</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/reviews/webflow-ai" class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">READ REVIEW ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-3">Best for: Personal projects, students. No time limit, just Webflow branding.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">ü•â Mixo - Free Landing Pages</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Quick landing pages, generous free tier</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/reviews/mixo-ai" class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">READ REVIEW ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-3">Best for: Lead gen pages, coming soon sites. Fastest setup, good free features.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">FAQs About Free Plans</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are free plans really free?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, with limitations. No credit card required for most. You can use them indefinitely, but with restrictions (no custom domain, builder branding).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I switch from free to paid later?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, always. Your content persists when upgrading. Often get first-year discounts when upgrading from free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do free plans hurt SEO?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Subdomains rank slightly worse than custom domains. Builder branding can look unprofessional. But for testing/personal projects, SEO impact is minimal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I remove builder branding on free?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">No. That's the main upsell driver. Branding removal requires paid plan on all major builders.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Start with Free, Upgrade When Ready</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Durable offers the most generous trial (30 days, full features). Test everything risk-free.</p>
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates.durable.affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates.durable.commission}
        label="Try Durable Free (30 Days)"
        className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-4">Or compare <a href="/reviews" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">all AI builder free trials</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
